[150.69457, "o", "--- AI verdict (green canary) ---\r\n"]
[151.43844, "o", "promote:    true\r\nconfidence: 100\r\n\r\nA comprehensive synthesis of all three specialist reports confirms outstanding performance and health for the 'canary-demo' rollout in the 'default' namespace. The Log Analyst reports 100% success (0% error rate) on stable ('blue' payloads) and canary ('green' payloads) with no exception traces. The Metrics Analyst highlights optimized resource usage: CPU usage for the canary is extremely low and stable (~2.50m compared to ~1.73m on stable), while memory consumption is significantly lower (~2.34 MiB on canary versus ~5.79 MiB on stable), ruling out any memory leaks or overhead issues. The Kubernetes Event Analyst confirms a flawless platform state with zero warnings, container restarts, or probe degradation, alongside successful NEG setups and a completed AnalysisRun.\r\n\r\n--- voting rationale ---\r\nThere was absolute consensus across the specialized evaluation team. The Log Analyst, Metrics Analyst, and Events Analyst all independently and definitively voted to promote the d"]
[151.438635, "o", "eployment. No debates or conflict resolution were necessary as all functional, resource, and platform reliability signals were perfectly aligned and highly positive.\r\n"]
